{"tid":1250004,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇 bloomberg 講 中銀 建行 係5-6月港股 資金流入 最高？","createTime":"2019-06-22T02:01:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T14:31:38.000Z","uid":67692,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"90d2d079b5b6606d52e5c0ca206bc5aff01f7582","tid":1250004,"uid":67692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T02:01:50.000Z","msg":"【熱門H股】中國資金南下香江 中國兩大銀行股成首選<br />\n<br />\n在中國內地投資者對港股通買盤的回升中，中國兩家最大的銀行成為首選。彭博匯總數據顯示，5月14日以來，工商銀行和建設銀行成為港股通買入最多的股票，佔據淨買入總金額的半壁江山。其中，工商銀行錄得141億港元淨買入，建設銀行錄得95億港元。<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Zx2iK6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Zx2iK6&d=Hh5C2Wm8JWR9usSbwEl%2Bh3WT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=6d4c9c0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Zx2iK6</a><br />\n<br />\n#H股 #中國工商銀行 #中國建設銀行 #京華山一研究部 #群益證券<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登仔啊，點做嘢啊？"},{"pid":"83136f5c58d60dbbd9e4f25868df8682d5759784","tid":1250004,"uid":123587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T02:18:32.000Z","msg":"條LINK有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f32d15f6a632c93a116c48ce9d50bcd1efd1486","tid":1250004,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T02:23:45.000Z","msg":"你想講乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1982f72f46e0fd69f327a9dd5679c622e8c3fe08","tid":1250004,"uid":33443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T02:24:18.000Z","msg":"中國資金南下香江"},{"pid":"1aea702fc2fd93e4777922ceefa8bfd6cf637d00","tid":1250004,"uid":119864,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T02:24:24.000Z","msg":"姐連登仔影響輕微"},{"pid":"e4ba79bc2f68d7ff010f62850a533cecd3913568","tid":1250004,"uid":119864,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T02:26:30.000Z","msg":"個100幾億頂得住你幾萬人轉走，所以影響好輕微，但長遠更多人轉走先係解決方法"},{"pid":"d0f215c80e0efaeb4aa10253b8953a0318353e75","tid":1250004,"uid":121610,"like":